-- Russian Brokerage Metropol Names Vodopyanov General Director
-- B y   B r a d   C o o k
-- 2011-12-28T12:40:15Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-28/russian-brokerage-metropol-names-vodopyanov-general-director.html
IFC Metropol, a Moscow-based
investment bank, named Yury Vodopyanov general director to
replace Mikhail Slipenchuk, who was elected to the State Duma,
the company said in a statement today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
